Class AbstractLocalizedSequence

java.lang.Object
  annotate.genome.sequence.AbstractLocalizedSequence
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
ComplexSequence, PointSequence, SimpleSequence
public abstract class AbstractLocalizedSequence
extends java.lang.Object
implements LocalizedSequence

Author:
jaschasilbermann An Abstract Localized Sequence provides minimal implementations for many of the methods in the Localized Sequence interface. Most importantly, the #compareTo(LocalizedSequence) method is implemented. Please note that specific implementations for the various overloaded #overlaps() methods are located in the more specific classes.
